data.description: This beautiful 3/2 split plan on a corner lot awaits your occupancy. This one has it all; wood floors in bedrooms and ceramic floors and counter tops throughout. formal dining and eat-in kithchen, family room with beautiful fireplace. Beautiful fixtures throughout. Master bedroom has dual vanities and separate shower with his and her closets. New roof with architectural shingles. Beautiful landscaping. This one is situated in the heart of Madison. Easy access to restaurants and shopping. Call your agent today for your private showing.
